      </section>
      
      <section class="section-block-markdown-cell">
      <p>Podemos definir o espaço entre as colunas e as linhas com a propriedade <code>grid-gap</code>.</p>
      <div class="highlight"><pre><span></span><span class="err">```</span><span class="nt">seção</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{opening_brace}</span><span class="w">    </span><span class="k">display</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="k">grid</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="err">```markdown</span>
