      <section class="section-block-markdown-cell">
      <h4 id="Justify-items">Justify-items<a class="anchor-link" href="#Justify-items"><img decoding="async" class="link-img" width="24px" height="24px" alt="link image 352" src={svg_paths.link_svg_path}/></a></h4>
      </section>
      
      <section class="section-block-markdown-cell">
      <p>Podemos alinhar os elementos no eixo X do <code>Grid</code> com a propriedade <code>justify-items</code>.
      Os valores que podemos utilizar são:</p>
      <ul>
      <li><code>start</code>: alinha os elementos no início do eixo principal.- <code>end</code>: alinha os elementos ao final do eixo principal.- <code>center</code>: alinha os elementos no centro do eixo principal.- <code>stretch</code>: estica os elementos para que ocupem todo o espaço disponível no eixo principal.</li>
      </ul>
      <div class="highlight"><pre><span></span>```<span class="p">&lt;</span><span class="nt">section</span><span class="p">&gt;&lt;</span><span class="nt">div</span><span class="p">&gt;</span>Texto 1<span class="p">&lt;/</span><span class="nt">div</span><span class="p">&gt;&lt;</span><span class="nt">div</span><span class="p">&gt;</span>Texto 2<span class="p">&lt;/</span><span class="nt">div</span><span class="p">&gt;&lt;</span><span class="nt">div</span><span class="p">&gt;</span>Texto 3<span class="p">&lt;/</span><span class="nt">div</span><span class="p">&gt;&lt;/</span><span class="nt">section</span><span class="p">&gt;</span>```
      ```css
      ```seção {    display: grid;    justify-items: center;}```
      </pre></div>
      </section>
      
      <section class="section-block-markdown-cell">
      <h4 id="Justify-self">Justify-self<a class="anchor-link" href="#Justify-self"><img decoding="async" class="link-img" width="24px" height="24px" alt="link image 353" src={svg_paths.link_svg_path}/></a></h4>
      </section>
      
      <section class="section-block-markdown-cell">
      <p>Com <code>justify-items</code> alinhamos todos os elementos no eixo principal do <code>Grid</code>, mas com <code>justify-self</code> podemos alinhar um elemento no eixo principal do <code>Grid</code> de forma diferente do resto dos elementos.</p>
      <div class="highlight"><pre><span></span><span class="p">&lt;</span><span class="nt">section</span><span class="p">&gt;</span>    <span class="p">&lt;</span><span class="nt">div</span><span class="p">&gt;</span>Texto 1<span class="p">&lt;/</span><span class="nt">div</span><span class="p">&gt;&lt;</span><span class="nt">div</span><span class="p">&gt;</span>Texto 2<span class="p">&lt;/</span><span class="nt">div</span><span class="p">&gt;</span>    <span class="p">&lt;</span><span class="nt">div</span><span class="p">&gt;</span>Texto 3<span class="p">&lt;/</span><span class="nt">div</span><span class="p">&gt;&lt;/</span><span class="nt">section</span><span class="p">&gt;</span>
      seção {    display: grid;    justify-items: center;}
      ```markdown
      section div:nth-child(2) {
      ```    justify-self: end;```markdown
      </pre></div>
      <pre><code>
      ![justify-self](data:image/png;base64,)</code></pre>
      </section>
      
      <section class="section-block-markdown-cell">
      <h4 id="Align-items">Align-items<a class="anchor-link" href="#Align-items"><img decoding="async" class="link-img" width="24px" height="24px" alt="link image 354" src={svg_paths.link_svg_path}/></a></h4>
      </section>
      
      <section class="section-block-markdown-cell">
      <p>É muito parecido com <code>justify-items</code>, mas em vez de alinhar os elementos no eixo X, os alinha no eixo Y.
      Os valores que podemos utilizar são:</p>
      <ul>
      <li><code>start</code>: alinha os elementos no início do eixo secundário.- <code>end</code>: alinha os elementos ao final do eixo secundário.- <code>center</code>: alinha os elementos no centro do eixo secundário.- <code>stretch</code>: estica os elementos para que ocupem todo o espaço disponível no eixo secundário.</li>
      </ul>
      <div class="highlight"><pre><span></span><span class="p">&lt;</span><span class="nt">section</span><span class="p">&gt;&lt;</span><span class="nt">div</span><span class="p">&gt;</span>Texto 1<span class="p">&lt;/</span><span class="nt">div</span><span class="p">&gt;&lt;</span><span class="nt">div</span><span class="p">&gt;</span>Texto 2<span class="p">&lt;/</span><span class="nt">div</span><span class="p">&gt;</span>
          <span class="p">&lt;</span><span class="nt">div</span><span class="p">&gt;</span>Texto 3<span class="p">&lt;/</span><span class="nt">div</span><span class="p">&gt;&lt;/</span><span class="nt">section</span><span class="p">&gt;</span>```
      </pre></div>
      <div class="highlight"><pre><span></span><span class="err">```</span><span class="nt">seção</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{opening_brace}</span><span class="err">```</span>
      <span class="k">display</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="k">grid</span><span class="p">;</span>
      <span class="err">```</span><span class="w">    </span><span class="k">align-items</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kc">center</span><span class="p">;{closing_brace}</span>
      </pre></div>
      </section>
      
      <section class="section-block-markdown-cell">
      <h4 id="Align-self">Align-self<a class="anchor-link" href="#Align-self"><img decoding="async" class="link-img" width="24px" height="24px" alt="link image 355" src={svg_paths.link_svg_path}/></a></h4>
      </section>
      
      <section class="section-block-markdown-cell">
      <p>Com <code>align-items</code> alinhamos todos os elementos no eixo secundário do <code>Grid</code>, mas com <code>align-self</code> podemos alinhar um elemento no eixo secundário do <code>Grid</code> de forma diferente do restante dos elementos.</p>
      <div class="highlight"><pre><span></span>&lt;section&gt;&lt;div&gt;Texto 1&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Texto 2&lt;/div&gt;```markdown
      &lt;div&gt;Texto 3&lt;/div&gt;
      ```&lt;/section&gt;```
      seção {    display: grid;    align-items: center;{
      
      section div:nth-child(2) {    align-self: end;{
      </pre></div>
      <img src="https://pub-fb664c455eca46a2ba762a065ac900f7.r2.dev/css0.webp" width="203" height="248" alt="image css 1" loading="lazy">
      </section>
      
      <section class="section-block-markdown-cell">
      <h4 id="Place-content">Place-content<a class="anchor-link" href="#Place-content"><img decoding="async" class="link-img" width="24px" height="24px" alt="link image 356" src={svg_paths.link_svg_path}/></a></h4>
      </section>
      
      <section class="section-block-markdown-cell">
      <p>Se quisermos usar <code>justify-content</code> e <code>align-content</code> ao mesmo tempo, podemos usar <code>place-content</code>.
      Os valores que podemos utilizar são:</p>
      <ul>
      <li><code>start</code>: alinha os elementos no início do eixo principal e secundário.- <code>end</code>: alinha os elementos no final do eixo principal e secundário.- <code>center</code>: alinha os elementos no centro do eixo principal e secundário.- <code>stretch</code>: estica os elementos para que ocupem todo o espaço disponível no eixo principal e secundário.</li>
      </ul>
      <p><code>html&lt;section&gt;&lt;div&gt;Texto 1&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Texto 2&lt;/div&gt; &lt;div&gt;Texto 3&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/section&gt;</code></p>
      <pre><code>```css
      ```secção {    display: grid;    place-content: center;}```</code></pre>
      </section>
      
      <section class="section-block-markdown-cell">
      <h3 id="Pr%C3%A1tica-de-Grid">Prática de Grid<a class="anchor-link" href="#Pr%C3%A1tica-de-Grid"><img decoding="async" class="link-img" width="24px" height="24px" alt="link image 357" src={svg_paths.link_svg_path}/></a></h3>
      </section>
      
      <section class="section-block-markdown-cell">
      <p>Um bom recurso para praticar Grid é <a href="https://cssgridgarden.com/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">Grid Garden</a>.</p>
      </section>
      
      <section class="section-block-markdown-cell">
      <h2 id="Centralizar-um-div">Centralizar um div<a class="anchor-link" href="#Centralizar-um-div"><img decoding="async" class="link-img" width="24px" height="24px" alt="link image 358" src={svg_paths.link_svg_path}/></a></h2>
      </section>
      
      <section class="section-block-markdown-cell">
      <p>Até agora vimos 3 formas de centralizar um <code>div</code>:</p>
      <ul>
      <li>Com <code>position: absolute</code>.- Com <code>display: flex</code>.- Com <code>display: grid</code>.</li>
      </ul>
      </section>
      
      <section class="section-block-markdown-cell">
      <h2 id="Anima%C3%A7%C3%B5es">Animações<a class="anchor-link" href="#Anima%C3%A7%C3%B5es"><img decoding="async" class="link-img" width="24px" height="24px" alt="link image 359" src={svg_paths.link_svg_path}/></a></h2>
      </section>
      
      <section class="section-block-markdown-cell">
      <p>Dentro das animações, existem dois tipos: as <code>transições</code> e as <code>animações</code>.</p>
      </section>
      
      <section class="section-block-markdown-cell">
      <h3 id="Transi%C3%A7%C3%B5es">Transições<a class="anchor-link" href="#Transi%C3%A7%C3%B5es"><img decoding="async" class="link-img" width="24px" height="24px" alt="link image 360" src={svg_paths.link_svg_path}/></a></h3>
      </section>
      
      <section class="section-block-markdown-cell">
      <p>Nas transições mudamos um elemento de um estado inicial para um estado alvo</p>
      </section>
      
      <section class="section-block-markdown-cell">
      <p>Suponhamos que temos o seguinte círculo
      <code>html&lt;div class="pulser"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</code>
      E seu CSS</p>
      <div class="highlight"><pre><span></span><span class="err">``````</span><span class="nt">markdown</span>
      <span class="p">.</span><span class="nc">pulser</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{opening_brace}</span>
      <span class="err">```</span><span class="w">    </span><span class="n">largura</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">30</span><span class="kt">px</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w">    </span><span class="k">height</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">30</span><span class="kt">px</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="err">```markdown</span>
      <span class="err">cor</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="err">de</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">fundo</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mh">#09f</span><span class="p">;</span>
      <span class="err">```</span><span class="w">    </span><span class="k">border-radius</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">50</span><span class="kt">%</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w">    </span><span class="k">position</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kc">relative</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="err">```markdown</span>
      <span class="p">{closing_brace}</span>
      </pre></div>
      <p>Os elementos de HTML podem ter estados, por exemplo o estado <code>hover</code>, que é quando o usuário passa o cursor por cima do elemento.
      .pulser:hover {escala: 2;
          background: roxo;    box-shadow: 0 0 10px purple;}</p>
      <pre><code></code></pre>
      <p>Ao usar <code>scale</code>, aumentamos o tamanho, mas ocupando o mesmo espaço; no entanto, se tivéssemos alterado o <code>width</code> e o <code>height</code>, o botão teria se movido de lugar.</p>
      </section>
      
      <section class="section-block-markdown-cell">
      <h4 id="Transi%C3%A7%C3%A3o">Transição<a class="anchor-link" href="#Transi%C3%A7%C3%A3o"><img decoding="async" class="link-img" width="24px" height="24px" alt="link image 361" src={svg_paths.link_svg_path}/></a></h4>
      </section>
      
      <section class="section-block-markdown-cell">
      <p>O que acontece é que, se agora passarmos o mouse por cima do círculo, o estado muda de repente; então, é aqui que entra a <code>transição</code>, que é como indicamos ao CSS como o estado deve ser modificado. Por exemplo, se quisermos que a transição dure 1 segundo</p>
      <div class="highlight"><pre><span></span><span class="err">```</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nc">pulser</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{opening_brace}</span><span class="w">    </span><span class="k">width</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">30</span><span class="kt">px</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w">    </span><span class="k">height</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">30</span><span class="kt">px</span><span class="p">;</span>
      <span class="w">    </span><span class="k">background-color</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mh">#09f</span><span class="p">;</span>
      <span class="w">    </span><span class="k">border-radius</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">50</span><span class="kt">%</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w">    </span><span class="k">position</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kc">relative</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w">    </span><span class="k">transition</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="kt">s</span><span class="p">;{closing_brace}</span><span class="err">```</span>
      </pre></div>
      </section>
      
      <section class="section-block-markdown-cell">
      <p>É importante colocar a transição em <code>.pulser</code> e não em <code>.pulser:hover</code> porque, caso contrário, a transição não se aplicaria ao voltar ao estado inicial. Ou seja, quando passarmos o mouse sobre o círculo, a transição será visível, mas quando retirarmos o mouse do círculo, não haverá uma transição de volta, mas sim uma mudança abrupta para o estado inicial.</p>
      </section>
      
      <section class="section-block-markdown-cell">
      <h4 id="O-que-se-quer-transicionar-transition-property">O que se quer transicionar transition-property<a class="anchor-link" href="#O-que-se-quer-transicionar-transition-property"><img decoding="async" class="link-img" width="24px" height="24px" alt="link image 362" src={svg_paths.link_svg_path}/></a></h4>
      </section>
      
      <section class="section-block-markdown-cell">
      <p>Com o anterior seria feita uma transição de cor, de tamanho e de fundo, mas se não quisermos que se produza uma transição de tudo podemos indicá-lo mediante <code>transition-property</code></p>
      <div class="highlight"><pre><span></span>.pulser {opening_brace}
      ```    largura: 30px;    height: 30px;    background-color: <span class="ni">#09f</span>;    border-radius: 50%;    position: relative;    transição: 1s;    transition-property: background-color, scale;```yaml
      transformers:
        library: sentence-transformers
        models:
      <span class="w">    </span><span class="k">-</span><span class="w"> </span>distiluse-base-multilingual-cased-v1
        pooling: 
          type: mean
        normalize: true
        embeddings_path: data/embeddings.pkl
      </pre></div>
      <p>Desta maneira, apenas a transição de <code>background-color</code> e <code>scale</code> será feita</p>
      </section>
      
      <section class="section-block-markdown-cell">
      <h4 id="Transi%C3%A7%C3%B5es-suaves">Transições suaves<a class="anchor-link" href="#Transi%C3%A7%C3%B5es-suaves"><img decoding="async" class="link-img" width="24px" height="24px" alt="link image 363" src={svg_paths.link_svg_path}/></a></h4>
      </section>
      
      <section class="section-block-markdown-cell">
      <p>A transição padrão é feita de maneira linear, mas se quisermos mudá-la podemos fazer isso através de <code>transition-timing-function</code></p>
      <div class="highlight"><pre><span></span><span class="err">```</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nc">pulsador</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{opening_brace}</span><span class="w">    </span><span class="k">width</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">30</span><span class="kt">px</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="k">height</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">30</span><span class="kt">px</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="err">```markdown</span>
      <span class="n">fundo-cor</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mh">#09f</span><span class="p">;</span>
      <span class="err">```</span><span class="w">    </span><span class="k">border-radius</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">50</span><span class="kt">%</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w">    </span><span class="k">position</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kc">relative</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w">    </span><span class="k">transition</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="kt">s</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w">    </span><span class="k">transition-property</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="k">background-color</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="k">scale</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w">    </span><span class="k">transition-timing-function</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kc">ease-in-out</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="err">{opening_brace}```</span>
      <span class="err">Dessa</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="err">forma,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="err">a</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="err">transição</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="err">será</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="err">mais</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="err">suave</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="err">no</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="err">início</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="err">e</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="err">no</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="err">final.</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="err">Os</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="err">valores</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="err">possíveis</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="err">são</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="err">os</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">seguintes</span><span class="p">:</span>
      <span class="w"> </span><span class="o">+</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kc">linear</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">+</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">facilidade</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">+</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kc">ease-in</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">+</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kc">ease-out</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">+</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kc">ease-in-out</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">+</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nb">cubic-bezier</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">n</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">n</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">n</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">n</span><span class="p">)</span>
      </pre></div>
      </section>
      
      <section class="section-block-markdown-cell">
      <h4 id="Transi%C3%A7%C3%B5es-por-etapas">Transições por etapas<a class="anchor-link" href="#Transi%C3%A7%C3%B5es-por-etapas"><img decoding="async" class="link-img" width="24px" height="24px" alt="link image 364" src={svg_paths.link_svg_path}/></a></h4>
      </section>
      
      <section class="section-block-markdown-cell">
      <p>Se queremos que a animação seja feita em vários passos, podemos usar <code>steps(n)</code>, onde <code>n</code> é o número de passos que queremos que a animação tenha.</p>
      <div class="highlight"><pre><span></span><span class="err">```</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nc">pulser</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{opening_brace}</span><span class="w">    </span><span class="k">width</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">30</span><span class="kt">px</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="err">```markdown</span>
      <span class="k">height</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">30</span><span class="kt">px</span><span class="p">;</span>
      <span class="err">```</span><span class="w">    </span><span class="k">background-color</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mh">#09f</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w">    </span><span class="k">border-radius</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">50</span><span class="kt">%</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w">    </span><span class="k">position</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kc">relative</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w">    </span><span class="k">transition</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="kt">s</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w">    </span><span class="k">transition-property</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="k">background-color</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="k">scale</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w">    </span><span class="k">transition-timing-function</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nb">steps</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mi">5</span><span class="p">);</span><span class="err">```markdown</span>
      <span class="p">{closing_brace}</span>
      </pre></div>
      <p>Desta forma, a transição será realizada em 5 etapas durante 1 segundo</p>
      </section>
      
      <section class="section-block-markdown-cell">
      <h4 id="Controle-total-da-transi%C3%A7%C3%A3o-com-cubic-bezier">Controle total da transição com cubic-bezier<a class="anchor-link" href="#Controle-total-da-transi%C3%A7%C3%A3o-com-cubic-bezier"><img decoding="async" class="link-img" width="24px" height="24px" alt="link image 365" src={svg_paths.link_svg_path}/></a></h4>
      </section>
      
      <section class="section-block-markdown-cell">
      <p>Para poder controlar perfeitamente a transição podemos usar <code>cubic-bezier(n,n,n,n)</code>, onde <code>n</code> é um número entre 0 e 1 que indica a posição do ponto no eixo X e Y
      .pulser {```markdown
          width: 30px;</p>
      <pre><code class="language-height:">height:
          background-color: #09f;    border-radius: 50%;    position: relative;    transition: 1s;    transition-property: background-color, scale;```markdown
      transition-timing-function: cubic-bezier(0.1, 0.7, 1.0, 0.1);
      ```}{</code></pre>
      </section>
      
      <section class="section-block-markdown-cell">
      <p>Com <code>delay</code> podemos indicar o tempo que tem que passar até que a transição comece</p>
      <div class="highlight"><pre><span></span><span class="err">```</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nc">pulser</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{opening_brace}</span><span class="w">    </span><span class="k">width</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">30</span><span class="kt">px</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w">    </span><span class="k">height</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="mi">30</span><span class="kt">px</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="err">```markdown</span>
